ad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺果度返都只係做自己野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有興趣嘅話可以留意奴工處，啲發展商/物管公司時不時都會咁樣出ad請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋靚仔靚女<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對</span></strong>有著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 🍇"},{"pid":"2e002284e26adc09ad9ac6e30538469df63accde","tid":500644,"uid":14190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:36:03.000Z","msg":"一至六full time 坐<br />\n六日返地盤"},{"pid":"e7099dbd50f350fade14b086264017ea269b12f2","tid":500644,"uid":14190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:36:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一至<span style=\"color: red;\">五</span>full time 坐<br />\n六返地盤</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2db2a7e2310389e013d4d1caf4b77ed06236b988","tid":500644,"uid":138803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:37:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>較早前講果份part time其實係新樓樓盤啲CS黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n售樓日會好撚忙，而且會要OT (當然份allowance都好肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n但完左果日，直至有新貨推出之前通常都會好得閒冇乜野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺果度返都只係做自己野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有興趣嘅話可以留意奴工處，啲發展商/物管公司時不時都會咁樣出ad請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋靚仔靚女<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對</span></strong>有著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 🍇</blockquote><br />\n咪姐係地産<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜鬼CS"},{"pid":"8